{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SentinelAttack}}
'''A_SentinelAttack'''<br />
(no parameters)

Fires a {{Class|SentinelFX2}} followed by eight {{Class|SentinelFX1}} making a trail, each distant from the previous by the measure of the lead actor's radius. Each trail actor has the same speed as the lead actor, and all nine take as their target the calling actor, as is customary with projectiles.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Sentinel}} and actors inheriting from it.

